<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Book Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center min-vh-100">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-8">
                <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-4">
                    <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-book-dead text-danger" style="font-size: 6rem;"></i>
                        </div>
                        
                        <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold text-danger mb-3">404</h1>
                        
                        <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-3">Kitap Bulunamadı</h2>
                        
                        <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-4">
                            Aradığınız kitap mevcut değil veya silinmiş olabilir.
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="alert alert-warning border-0 rounded-3 mb-4" role="alert">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                            <strong>Not:</strong> Kitap veritabanında bulunamadı.
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="d-grid gap-3 mt-4">
                            <a href="/books" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-3 fw-semibold">
                                <i class="fas fa-book me-2"></i>Kitap Listesine Git
                            </a>
                            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg rounded-3 fw-semibold">
                                <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Ana Sayfaya Dön
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="card-footer bg-light border-0 py-3 text-center rounded-bottom-4">
                        <small class="text-muted">
                            <i class="fas fa-question-circle me-2"></i>
                            Yardıma mı ihtiyacınız var? Lütfen yöneticinizle iletişime geçin.
                        </small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>